# Screenshots directory
This directory will contain screenshots captured during test execution.
Screenshots are automatically taken when tests fail or when explicitly requested.

## Structure
- Screenshots are organized by test execution timestamp
- Filenames include browser, device, and test case information
- Failed test screenshots are prefixed with "failure-"
- Manual screenshots are prefixed with "manual-"

## Cleanup
Screenshots should be periodically cleaned up to avoid excessive disk usage.
Consider implementing a retention policy based on age or test run count.